                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Each creature in the tormented's Tortured Gaze aura takes [[/r {14d6}[mental]]]{14d6 mental damage} (@Check[type:will|dc:34|basic:true]). A creature that fails is also @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1} (or @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 2} on a critical failure).</p>\n<p>The tormented can't Scream in Agony again for [[/br 1d4 #Scream in Agony Recharge]]{1d4 rounds}, but recharges the ability whenever they take damage from an attacker's critical hit or their own critical failure on a saving throw.</p>"
